Development of travel prices since 1989
Until 1989, there were only five licensed state travel agencies in the then <0xC4><0x8C>SSR: <0xC4><0x8C>edok, sporturist, CKM, recrea and autoturist.
At the time, the travel agencies mainly only sold trips to the socialist Eastern Bloc countries, while in the West only selected people were allowed.
